Kyle's functional requirements:
Should be able to create a new profile
Load a save profile
Change characters or boards
Pause the game, quit/exit the game, and restart the game.
Kyle's non-functional requirements:
Main Menu should not take more than seven seconds to load
Account information (passwords and payment info) should all be encrypted to the highest degree
The system and server should support at least 250,000 users at any given time - worldwide.

